<body>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10542" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="NEW">New Address Block</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10546" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Specify the placement of address data fields for an address block for <link href="text/swriter/01/mm_seladdblo.xhp">mail merge</link>.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10569" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Address Elements</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1056D" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Select a field and drag it to the other list box.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10570" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">&gt;</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10574" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Click to add the selected field from the Address Elements list to the other list box. You can add the same field at multiple positions.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10577" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">&lt;</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1057B" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Click to remove the selected field from the other list box.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1057E" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Drag address element to the field below</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10582" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Arrange the fields by drag-and-drop or use the buttons in the 4-arrows-block.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10585" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Preview</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10589" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Shows a preview of the first database record using the current address block layout.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1058C" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">(4 arrows block)</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10590" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Select an entry in the list box and click a button to move the entry.</paragraph>
</body>
